00:12:58.577 --> 00:12:59.912 line:95%,end
They both want to do it.

00:12:59.979 --> 00:13:01.614 line:95%,end
You know, Mackenzie wants to--

00:13:01.680 --> 00:13:03.549 line:95%,end
she wants to really step
it up with her dancing.

00:13:03.616 --> 00:13:05.551 line:95%,end
But I'll miss my school friends.

00:13:05.618 --> 00:13:07.253 line:95%,end
I know. You have your best friend there,
huh?

00:13:07.319 --> 00:13:10.623 line:95%,end
MACKENZIE: I want to be homeschooled,
but I'll miss my friends.

00:13:10.689 --> 00:13:16.128 line:95%,end
TRACY: I suggest maybe me and you going
to a meeting with one of the counselors.

00:13:16.195 --> 00:13:18.297 line:95%,end
MELISSA: This sounds good,
so we're going to move forward.

00:13:18.364 --> 00:13:20.399 line:95%,end
OK, girls, we got to go get ready
for dance.

00:13:20.466 --> 00:13:21.901 line:95%,end
Thank Tracy for coming.

00:13:21.967 --> 00:13:22.968 line:95%,end
Thank you.

00:13:23.035 --> 00:13:24.203 line:95%,end
You're welcome, girls.

00:13:24.603 --> 00:13:27.273 line:5%,start
[music playing]

00:13:31.076 --> 00:13:32.511 line:95%,end
Well, I'm excited for your solo.

00:13:32.611 --> 00:13:34.980 line:5%,start
It's been a really long,
rough road for Chloe.

00:13:35.047 --> 00:13:38.617 line:95%,end
Because Abby has said that she
no longer is at Maddie's level,

00:13:38.684 --> 00:13:41.153 line:95%,end
and that she can't keep up,
and she's regressed.

00:13:41.220 --> 00:13:45.124 line:95%,end
So I'm really happy to see Chloe
given the opportunity to prove

00:13:45.191 --> 00:13:46.926 line:95%,end
that none of that is true.

00:13:46.992 --> 00:13:48.460 line:95%,end
Come on, girls!
Let's go, let's go, let's go.

00:13:48.527 --> 00:13:50.029 line:95%,end
You should be ready!

