00:16:38.030 --> 00:16:39.164 line:95%,end
I think enough people--
HOLLY: Really?

00:16:39.264 --> 00:16:40.833 line:95%,end
--that are important know
how my daughter dances.

00:16:40.899 --> 00:16:41.934 line:95%,end
Yeah.

00:16:42.001 --> 00:16:46.405 line:95%,end
Asia might be a big deal on the internet,
but so was a dog who can bark his ABCs.

00:16:46.472 --> 00:16:50.342 line:95%,end
I never heard of Asia before
she walked through this door.

00:16:50.442 --> 00:16:54.046 line:95%,end
I just think that's a really
big thing to say.

00:16:54.113 --> 00:16:57.149 line:95%,end
The competitions that we do
in other states are larger.

00:16:57.216 --> 00:17:01.387 line:95%,end
I'm just mainly stating a fact that the
women up here did not know who Asia was.

00:17:01.487 --> 00:17:02.688 line:95%,end
There's nothing to disagree about.

00:17:02.755 --> 00:17:04.456 line:95%,end
I didn't even know who Nia was.

00:17:04.890 --> 00:17:06.325 line:95%,end
But I wouldn't expect you to.

00:17:06.392 --> 00:17:09.661 line:95%,end
All of the moms have worked really hard to
get our girls where they are in this team.

00:17:09.728 --> 00:17:13.365 line:95%,end
