and act like she's a star--

00:17:13.465 --> 00:17:15.501 line:95%,end
it's pretty obnoxious, to say the least.

00:17:15.567 --> 00:17:18.470 line:95%,end
I'm not afraid to say
anything at any time.

00:17:18.537 --> 00:17:20.739 line:95%,end
I don't care what you say
and what you don't say.

00:17:20.839 --> 00:17:22.741 line:95%,end
