00:17:23.509 --> 00:17:26.578 line:95%,end
Sometimes we have nothing interesting
or intelligent to say.

00:17:26.645 --> 00:17:27.579 line:95%,end
You should just be quiet.

00:17:27.646 --> 00:17:29.081 line:95%,end
