that that flag represents.

00:18:23.936 --> 00:18:25.037 line:95%,end
Absolutely.

00:18:25.104 --> 00:18:27.873 line:5%,start
CHRISTI: And for us to be like,
"Cover your booty with it"--

00:18:27.940 --> 00:18:30.876 line:5%,start
There are some things you just do not do.

00:18:30.943 --> 00:18:36.014 line:95%,end
And tampering-- destroying the
American flag is one of them.

00:18:36.081 --> 00:18:37.649 line:95%,end
